# Numeric canary: the positive control for the numerical (`ref`) oracle. Under
# --oracle ref it FAILs on even n (a deliberate shape-dependent wrong answer)
# and PASSes on odd n; under --oracle diff it PASSes (the wrong value is never
# checked) -- proving the ref oracle catches what memory/diff oracles miss.
mojo_test(
    name = "fuzz_numeric_canary.mojo.test",
    size = "small",
